column4: Apple lawsuits against Qualcomm can proceed  U.S. judge rules
column5: Apple Inc's  11 foreign lawsuits against Qualcomm Inc  can proceed while the company's dispute plays out in the United States  a U.S. federal judge in San Diego ruled Sept. 7.
